---
description: Specifies testing guidelines for Flutter projects, covering unit, widget, and integration tests.
globs: test/**/*.dart
---
- Write unit tests for business logic in the domain layer.
- Implement widget tests for reusable UI components and pages.
- Use integration tests to validate full user flows across features.
- Apply mocking strategies with packages like mocktail or Mockito.
- Track and improve code coverage using proper tooling.
- Use descriptive test names and follow consistent naming conventions.
- Integrate tests into your CI/CD pipeline to ensure automated validation.
